Another Mandela royal is on the way.Mandla Mandela and his wife Rabia Mandela are expecting their first baby. We are excited beyond words today to be celebrating not only our first wedding anniversary but also the fact that we are expecting our first bundle of joy.Mvezo Komkhulu will once again experience the pitter-patter of a young Mandela s feet. It s been an amazing year. We are truly blessed, and very grateful for all the well wishes received, the couple announced in a joint statement yesterday.The couple tied the knot at a private ceremony in Cape Town early last year.Mandla is a grandson of former president Nelson Mandela and the chief of the Mvezo in the Eastern Cape.This is his fourth marriage. His marriage to Rabia was widely criticised especially by traditionalists.-TNA Reporter